                <li><strong>Full customization</strong> - Complete control over thresholds and interface</li>
                <li><strong>Rails-native</strong> - Built specifically for Rails with deep framework integration</li>
              </ul>
              <p>Perfect for development, staging, and cost-conscious production monitoring.</p>
            </div>
          </details>
